      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the pareidolia thing but it doesnt feel like its just in my head. it feels physical. like when the signal hits, it's almost like a low hum in the back of my mind. like something is trying to sync up with my brain waves. dont you think it's weird that the stars in the belt are so perfectly spaced while everything else in the sky is basically chaotic?",
